M|rules|title: Optimize SVG Precision
M|rules|impact: LOW
M|rules|impactDescription: reduces file size
M|rules|tags: rendering, svg, optimization, svgo
M|rules|Reduce SVG coordinate precision to decrease file size. The optimal precision depends on the viewBox size, but in general reducing precision should be considered.
M|rules|**Incorrect (excessive precision):**
M|rules|```svg
M|rules|<path d="M 10.293847 20.847362 L 30.938472 40.192837" />
M|rules|```
M|rules|**Correct (1 decimal place):**
M|rules|```svg
M|rules|<path d="M 10.3 20.8 L 30.9 40.2" />
M|rules|```
M|rules|**Automate with SVGO:**
M|rules|```bash
M|rules|npx svgo --precision=1 --multipass icon.svg
M|rules|```